# Boundary Data Directory

This directory should contain administrative boundary files for the Barcelona Metropolitan Area.

## Required files:
- `amb_boundary.shp` - AMB administrative boundary
- `municipalities.shp` - Municipal boundaries within AMB
- `districts.shp` - District boundaries (optional)

## Data sources:
- AMB (Àrea Metropolitana de Barcelona) official website
- Institut Cartogràfic i Geològic de Catalunya (ICGC)
- OpenStreetMap administrative boundaries
- Generalitat de Catalunya data portal

## File format requirements:
- Shapefile (.shp) with associated files (.shx, .dbf, .prj)
- CRS: EPSG:25831 (UTM Zone 31N) preferred
- Include NAME/NOM field for municipality names

## Download links:
- AMB Open Data: https://opendata.amb.cat/
- ICGC: https://www.icgc.cat/
- OpenStreetMap: https://download.geofabrik.de/
